WEBVTT

00:00:08.004 --> 00:00:09.922
The year is 1194.

00:00:09.922 --> 00:00:12.800
Maurice De Bracy, 
enemy to the English crown,

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:15.928
is locked in combat
with a mysterious Black Knight.

00:00:16.304 --> 00:00:18.598
Suddenly, the Black Knight
gains the upper hand.

00:00:18.598 --> 00:00:21.726
He whispers his true identity
in De Bracy’s ear:

00:00:21.893 --> 00:00:24.520
King Richard the Lionheart of England.

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:26.314
De Bracy yields.

00:00:26.773 --> 00:00:31.819
Later, De Bracy offers to let King Richard
use his army of “Free Lances,”